replies.body:
Was personally banned for using "cheats" which I have miserably tried to prove wrong, but ended up getting the same auto-reply message, so there was literally 0 chances of me trying to get myself unbanned no matter how hard I tried to appeal the ban.

If Riot would give me just one chance to prove to them that I was a clean player, I'd be extremely thankful, but again, trying with them is useless as you'll always get the SAME message, no matter what you say.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}
